Package com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.value

Interface LongValued

All Superinterfaces:
Zeroable
All Known Subinterfaces:
Arithmetic<Value>, DoubleValued, FormattedLongValued, Identifiable, LengthOfTime<Duration>, Maximizable<Value>, Minimizable<Value>, Numeric<Value>, PointInTime<Time,Duration>, TimeMeasurement
Functional Interface:
This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
@FunctionalInterface public interface LongValued extends Zeroable
An object that has a long representation
